text: a l laoh poum mean botr laey haeyka poum mean mcheasa na del trauv korp sakkar da pitabrakd ruom cheamuoynung trong der . brasenbae mean men mcheasa ni muoy pitchea noam yk tow krobkrong nouv avei delke ban bangkeut haey puokke nung yk brieb leu knea towvinhtowmk( knong kar krobkrong) . a l laoh mha saatasam ampi avei del puokke niyeay bradit noh
